在碰撞前该车辆数据长时间掉线，存在小电瓶长时间断开的情况；随后，小电瓶再次被接通。在碰撞时，国家监控平台数据缺失，小电瓶已处于断电状态。“我们无法确认在此过程中小电瓶再次上电时，是否按照标准锁紧电极，也无法排除因装配不当导致碰撞后小电瓶断电的可能。”小米汽车称。小米汽车回应博主用SU7与极氪007对撞测试：设置不严谨、记录不完整、结论不科学 | 每经网 (nbd.com.cn)"},"attached_info":"Cj8I9c/06Z6/yKFfEAMaCTEwOTkxOTQ5MSDdgfi1BjAAOEhABHIJNjY0Mzg4NzcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"147 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fad1445df169b026de83084d8753ac09_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1723785458.301329","card_id":"Q_664426192","target":{"id":664426192,"title":"如何看待 2024 年 8 月 16 日 A 股的市场行情？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664426192","type":"question","created":1723771595,"answer_count":70,"follower_count":74,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3217,6723,34239,105508,583465],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如题。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I9c/06Z6/yKFfEAMaCTEwOTkyNzc4NCDL1fq1BjAAOEpABXIJNjY0NDI2MTkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"123 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-114d75c2c6306a7d72cadac800c383fc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1723785458.301685","card_id":"Q_52764815","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":52764815,"title":"电影《罗生门》中谁的故事更可信？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/52764815","type":"question","created":1479484777,"answer_count":18,"follower_count":90,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,6182,22889,26817,184444],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt